The analog expansion connector is
explained in much more detail in

189
00:14:22.060 --> 00:14:28.120
the stereo connector application note
available on developer.qualcomm.com.

190
00:14:28.120 --> 00:14:30.280
This isn't a link
directly to the App Note,

191
